      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just... they have their own lives to live, you know? their jobs, their own families. and then there's me, needing help with the little things, or just being a constant worry for them. sometimes i look at them and i just wish i could give them their freedom back. like, if i wasn't here, they wouldn't have to carry all this weight anymore. wouldn't that be a relief for them?",
