      "content": "but that's just putting more weight on them... having to stay because they feel they have to. it feels so selfish of me to keep holding them back just because i'm scared. sometimes i think the most loving thing i could actually do is just... let go. just stop being a problem for them to solve. dont you think they deserve that peace?",
